{"tid":1604354,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"當勇武人手裝備武力都唔夠對方黎，係咪應該唔好再打陣地戰？","createTime":"2019-09-30T02:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T04:24:18.000Z","uid":48093,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"914dd46f4f719591b5cd6ec05812025967d34813","tid":1604354,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:44:57.000Z","msg":"每一次玩陣地戰都係死守係幾條街<br />\n對方就不停放TG、玩突擊<br />\n再被對方大把時間玩圍捕<br />\n而我地每次就不停咁向前向後逃跑<br />\n好似被對方玩弄咁<br />\n被人熟哂我地套路<br />\n又長時間用左黎逃亡<br />\n而每次都好多人被捕<br />\n<br />\n點解唔轉下玩法？<br />\n打遊擊 Hit and Run<br />\n係有限資源做最多既野<br />\n係對方黎到前就走<br />\n唔駛同佢地硬碰<br />\n而我地又可以減低受傷同被捕風險"},{"pid":"4841ebd9748f44f33579e31b05a6060770a6ffd0","tid":1604354,"uid":258696,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:46:42.000Z","msg":"次次都打陣地戰架啦<br />\n<br />\n情意結<br />\n<br />\n勇武又話要保護和理非<br />\n<br />\n明明應該無和理非大圍人比勇武躲入去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0122f74c98f197e9145ef9916a5da8c9b3cf6afa","tid":1604354,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:47:50.000Z","msg":"不如塞返機場？"},{"pid":"74175a056c026c6890a8827320d8d0a0512608a7","tid":1604354,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:47:50.000Z","msg":"利用高樓大廈特點"},{"pid":"0d76425b6f57922c9abad666bbd87d46ba07d061","tid":1604354,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:48:47.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻阻你<br />\n[緊急要人]  全 港 今 晚 貼 街 招 ！ ！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604312\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604312</a>"},{"pid":"4332a9904895e2b27da0211c8cb7c5e58f889964","tid":1604354,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:49:59.000Z","msg":"目前大局已定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ab659c6542b2339f622cce58bbcfe94a61cc6c","tid":1604354,"uid":114122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite